units lj
dimension 3
atom_style sph
boundary p p p
lattice fcc 0.8442
region box block 0 6 0 6 0 6
create_box 1 box
create_atoms 1 box
mass 1 1.0
set group all sph/e 1.0
set group all sph/rho 0.8442
pair_style sph/lj
pair_coeff * * 1.0 2.4
fix 1 all sph
timestep 0.0001
thermo 5
thermo_style custom step temp epair etotal press
thermo_modify format float %20.15g
run 20
